    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aerophones in which an air stream is directed against a reed, setting the reed in periodic vibration that interrupts the stream intermittently.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
